{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8370-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"50901"},"text":"§ 50901.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Confidentiality of peer support communications","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8371-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definitions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this section:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8372-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Law enforcement agency","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “law enforcement agency” means a Federal agency that employs a law enforcement officer.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8373-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Law enforcement officer","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “law enforcement officer” has the meaning given the term “Federal law enforcement officer” in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t18/s115"},"text":"section 115 of title 18","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8374-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Peer support communication","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The term “peer support communication” includes—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8375-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an oral or written communication made in the course of a peer support counseling session;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8376-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a note or report arising out of a peer support counseling session;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8377-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/3/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a record of a peer support counseling session; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8378-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/3/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" with respect to a communication made by a peer support participant in the course of a peer support counseling session, another communication, regarding the first communication, that is made between a peer support specialist and—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8379-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/3/D/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" another peer support specialist;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f837a-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/3/D/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a staff member of a peer support counseling program; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f837b-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/3/D/iii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iii"},"text":"(iii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a supervisor of the peer support specialist.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f837c-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Peer support counseling program","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “peer support counseling program” means a program provided by a law enforcement agency that provides counseling services from a peer support specialist to a law enforcement officer of the agency.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f837d-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Peer support counseling session","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “peer support counseling session” means any counseling formally provided through a peer support counseling program between a peer support specialist and 1 or more law enforcement officers.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f837e-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Peer support participant","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “peer support participant” means a law enforcement officer who receives counseling services from a peer support specialist.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f837f-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7"},"text":"(7)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Peer support specialist","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The term “peer support specialist” means a law enforcement officer who—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8380-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/7/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" has received training in—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8381-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/7/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" peer support counseling; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8382-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/7/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" providing emotional and moral support to law enforcement officers who have been involved in or exposed to an emotionally traumatic experience in the course of employment; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8383-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/a/7/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" is designated by a law enforcement agency to provide the services described in subparagraph (A).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8384-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Prohibition","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Except as provided in subsection (c), a peer support specialist or a peer support participant may not disclose the contents of a peer support communication to an individual who was not a party to the peer support communication.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8385-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Exceptions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Subsection (b) shall not apply to a peer support communication if—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8386-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" the peer support communication contains—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8387-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" an explicit threat of suicide by an individual in which the individual—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8388-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" shares—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subclause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8389-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/A/i/I"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"I"},"text":"(I)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an intent to die by suicide; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subclause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f838a-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/A/i/II"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"II"},"text":"(II)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a plan for a suicide attempt or the means by which the individual plans to carry out a suicide attempt; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f838b-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" does not solely share that the individual is experiencing suicidal thoughts;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f838c-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an explicit threat by an individual of imminent and serious physical bodily harm or death to another individual;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f838d-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" information—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f838e-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/C/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" relating to the abuse or neglect of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subclause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f838f-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/C/i/I"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"I"},"text":"(I)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a child; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subclause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8390-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/C/i/II"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"II"},"text":"(II)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an older or vulnerable individual; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8391-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/C/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" that is required by law to be reported; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8392-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/1/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an admission of criminal conduct;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8393-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" the disclosure is permitted by each peer support participant who was a party to, as applicable—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8394-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the peer support communication;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8395-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the peer support counseling session out of which the peer support communication arose;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8396-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/2/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the peer support counseling session of which the peer support communication is a record; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8397-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/2/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the communication made in the course of a peer support counseling session that the peer support communication is regarding;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8398-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a court of competent jurisdiction issues an order or subpoena requiring the disclosure of the peer support communication; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f8399-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/c/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the peer support communication contains information that is required by law to be disclosed.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f839a-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Rule of construction","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Nothing in subsection (b) shall be construed to prohibit the disclosure of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f839b-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an observation made by a law enforcement officer of a peer support participant outside of a peer support counseling session; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f839c-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" knowledge of a law enforcement officer about a peer support participant not gained from a peer support communication.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f839d-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s50901/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Disclosure of rights","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Before the initial peer support counseling session of a peer support participant, a peer support specialist shall inform the peer support participant in writing of the confidentiality requirement under subsection (b) and the exceptions to the requirement under subsection (c).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id4d5f839e-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/60/s2"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–60, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2021-11-18"},"text":"Nov. 18, 2021","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/135/1470"},"text":"135 Stat. 1470","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id4d5f839f-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id4d5f83a0-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"shortTitle","id":"id4d5f83a1-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Short Title","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For short title of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/60"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–60","children":[],"tail":", which is classified to this chapter, as the “Confidentiality Opportunities for Peer Support Counseling Act” and also as the “COPS Counseling Act”, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/60/s1"},"text":"section 1 of Pub. L. 117–60","children":[],"tail":", set out as a Short Title of 2021 Amendment note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s10101"},"text":"section 10101 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
